---
import { BASE_URL } from "../../configs/constant.conf";

interface Props {
  title: string;
  full_description: string;
  data: Map<string, string>;
}
const { title, full_description, data }: Props = Astro.props;
---

<div class="card card-product card-plain">
  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-12">
      {title.length != 0 && <h2 class="mb-3">{title}</h2>}
      {
        full_description.length != 0 && (
          <p class="mb-5 w-lg-70">{full_description}</p>
        )
      }

      <div class="nav-wrapper position-relative end-0 pb-4 border-bottom">
        <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-fill p-1 w-lg-50" role="tablist">
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a
              class="nav-link mb-0 px-0 py-1 active"
              data-bs-toggle="tab"
              href="#first-tab"
              role="tab"
              aria-controls="material"
              aria-selected="true"
            >
              Material
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a
              class="nav-link mb-0 px-0 py-1"
              data-bs-toggle="tab"
              href="#second-tab"
              role="tab"
              aria-controls="function"
              aria-selected="false"
            >
              Function
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a
              class="nav-link mb-0 px-0 py-1"
              data-bs-toggle="tab"
              href="#third-tab"
              role="tab"
              aria-controls="warranty"
              aria-selected="false"
            >
              Warranty
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a
              class="nav-link mb-0 px-0 py-1"
              data-bs-toggle="tab"
              href="#fourth-tab"
              role="tab"
              aria-controls="instructions"
              aria-selected="false"
            >
              Instructions
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="tab-content tab-space">
        <div
          class="tab-pane active show"
          id="first-tab"
          role="tabpanel"
          aria-labelledby="#material"
        >
          <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4 pe-lg-10">
              <h5 class="mt-5 mb-4">Material</h5>
              <p>
                If everything I did failed - which it doesn't, it actually
                succeeds - just the fact that I'm willing to fail is an
                inspiration. People are so scared to lose that they don't even
                try.
                <br /><br />
                Like, one thing people can't say is that I'm not trying, and I'm
                not trying my hardest, and I'm not trying to do the best way I know
                how.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-6 mb-4">
                  <img
                    class="w-100 rounded-3"
                    src={`${BASE_URL}/images/product10.jpg`}
                    alt=""
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 mb-4">
                  <img
                    class="w-100 rounded-3"
                    src={`${BASE_URL}/images/product11.jpg`}
                    alt=""
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 mb-4">
                  <img
                    class="w-100 rounded-3"
                    src={`${BASE_URL}/images/product12.jpg`}
                    alt=""
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                  <img
                    class="w-100 rounded-3"
                    src={`${BASE_URL}/images/product13.jpg`}
                    alt=""
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="tab-pane"
          id="second-tab"
          role="tabpanel"
          aria-labelledby="#function"
        >
          <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4">
              <h5 class="mt-5 mb-4">Function</h5>
              <p>
                The time is now for it to be okay to be great. People in this
                world shun people for being great. For being a bright color. For
                standing out. But the time is now to be okay to be the greatest
                you.
                <br />
                Would you believe in what you believe in, if you were the only one
                who believed it? People are so scared to lose that they don't even
                try.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4">
              <img
                class="w-100 rounded-3"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611186871348-b1ce696e52c9?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
                alt=""
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="tab-pane"
          id="third-tab"
          role="tabpanel"
          aria-labelledby="#warranty"
        >
          <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4">
              <h5 class="mt-5 mb-4">Warranty</h5>
              <p>
                I always felt like I could do anything. That’s the main thing
                people are controlled by! Thoughts- their perception of
                themselves! They're slowed down by their perception of
                themselves.
                <br /><br />
                If you're taught you can’t do anything, you won’t do anything. I
                was taught I could do everything.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4">
              <img
                class="w-100 rounded-3"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494438639946-1ebd1d20bf85?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
                alt=""
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="tab-pane"
          id="fourth-tab"
          role="tabpanel"
          aria-labelledby="#instructions"
        >
          <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4">
              <h5 class="mt-5 mb-4">Instructions</h5>
              <p>
                We’re not always in the position that we want to be at. We’re
                constantly growing. We’re constantly making mistakes. We’re
                constantly trying to express ourselves and actualize our dreams.
                <br />
                If you have the opportunity to play this game of life you need to
                appreciate every moment. A lot of people don’t appreciate the moment
                until it’s passed.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-lg-0 mb-4">
              <img
                class="w-100 rounded-3"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611849362103-5c99622adf18?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
                alt=""
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
